Feature: Extract function

  Scenario: Simple function declaration
    Given I insert:
    """
    function abc() {
        console.log("abc");
    }
    """
    And I turn on js2-mode and js2-refactor-mode
    When I select "console.log"
    And I press "C-c C-m ef name RET"
    Then I should see:
    """
    function name() {
        console.log("abc");
    }

    function abc() {
        name();
    }
    """

  Scenario: Simple function assignment
    Given I insert:
    """
    var abc = function () {
        console.log("abc");
    }
    """
    And I turn on js2-mode and js2-refactor-mode
    When I select "console.log"
    And I press "C-c C-m ef name RET"
    Then I should see:
    """
    function name() {
        console.log("abc");
    }

    var abc = function () {
        name();
    }
    """

