  Scenario: Keep reference to var if in use
    Given I insert:
    """
    function abc(num) {
        var inc = 1;
        inc = inc + 7;
        return num + inc;
    }
    """
    And I turn on js2-mode and js2-refactor-mode
    When I go to the front of the word "var"
    And I set the mark
